@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_mvxuvc(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = ((0.39 + wp.cos(v1 + 0.81)) - (0.91 + v1))
    tmp = ((wp.cos(tmp + 0.95) + 0.84) / wp.exp((v2 + 0.24 / v0 + 0.42)))
    v1 = (wp.abs((tmp + 0.09 / v2 + 0.58)) + v0)
    data[tid] = v0
